<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="section section-gray" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Is this webinar really free?
          <svg class="faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, this webinar is completely free. No credit card required, no hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Will there be a recording?
          <svg class="faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, all registered attendees will receive a recording of the webinar within 24 hours after the live session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What if I can't attend live?
          <svg class="faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>No problem! Register anyway and we'll send you the recording. However, we encourage live attendance for the Q&A session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          What platform will the webinar be on?
          <svg class="faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>The webinar will be hosted on Zoom. You'll receive the join link before the session starts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Who is this webinar for?
          <svg class="faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>This webinar is for students (high school and college), parents wanting to support their children, educators, and anyone interested in understanding student mental health.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question">
          Will my privacy be protected?
          <svg class="faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Absolutely. Cameras are optional, and you can participate as you're comfortable. All discussions are confidential and judgment-free.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

